<L>__{exterior victor pascow and friends morning}
<A>__{pascow is in a blanket that is being carried by three boys and one girl. they are all yelling at each other not to joggle him, not to drop him. a small knot of horrified college kids moves with the bearers. pascow's head is upside down to the camera, which retreats ahead of the advancing students. fixed eyes stare. half of his head has been shattered inward. before the catastrophe he was a husky male of about twenty. he's dressed in a u of m muscle shirt and red jogging shorts. the camera pulls jerkily to one side, allowing the bearers to mount the steps of a brick building. the infirmary. the lookers on break to either side. the infirmary doors open.}
